 Router 端 JWT 签发与认证 | 互补关系：Router 签发 → PicoD 验证，形成完整认证链路 |\n  Line 176: - 验证逻辑与 AR-011 Router AuthMiddleware 模式统一\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/proposal.md:\n  Line 25: - JWT 密钥对的生成和管理（由 Router 组件负责，通过 K8s Secret `picod-router-identity` 存储）\n  Line 84: | Router JWT 密钥对 | RSA 私钥用于签发 token，公钥存储在 K8s Secret `picod-router-identity` |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-011/tasks.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-011 任务清单\n  Line 4: > **AR**: AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-011: Router JWT 认证与签发 — Delta Spec\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-011/design.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-011: Router JWT 认证与签发 — 设计说明\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-011: Router JWT 认证与签发\n  Line 9: - **AR**: AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/design.md:\n  Line 611: | AR-011 | WebSocket/gRPC 代理支持 | P2 |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/design.md:\n  Line 12: - WorkloadManager **不** 负责 JWT 鉴权（Router 层负责）、Redis 状态管理（Session Store 负责）或代码执行（PicoD 负责）\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md:\n  Line 53: - JWT 认证和鉴权（Router 层负责，WorkloadManager 通过 in-cluster ServiceAccount 信任）\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/design.md:\n  Line 70: | Extra env (JSON via `--set-json`) | Workload manager: `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`, `JWT_KEY_SECRET_NAMESPACE=agentcube`; Router: `RE