{"type":"text","timestamp":1775852393736,"sessionID":"ses_286f45fe3ffeXGNmZSBkPp1xxp","part":{"id":"prt_d790cecfd001UZ7Wi5LxckACmq","messageID":"msg_d790ce4f30016sk6Y067e9xUT8","sessionID":"ses_286f45fe3ffeXGNmZSBkPp1xxp","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-011 implementation in the agentcube project:\n\n## **AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发**\n\n### **Completed (已完成)**\n\n✅ **T-001**: JWTConfig 结构体与 Config 扩展\n- JWTConfig 结构体定义 (Expiration, Issuer, Leeway)\n- Config 扩展字段 (JWTExpiration, JWTIssuer, JWTLeeway)\n- NewDefaultConfig() 默认值设置\n- config_test.go 测试覆盖\n\n✅ **T-002**: JWTManager 构造函数支持配置注入\n- NewJWTManager(config *JWTConfig) 支持可选配置\n- nil 配置回退默认值\n- GenerateToken() 使用配置参数\n\n✅ **T-003**: JWTManager.PublicKey() 访问器\n- PublicKey() 方法实现\n- 线程安全返回公钥\n\n✅ **T-004**: JWTManager.ParseAndValidateToken() 方法\n- RS256 签名验证\n- exp/iat/iss claim 校验\n- Leeway 宽容窗口支持\n- 错误语义区分 (expired/invalid signature/invalid issuer/malformed)\n- 完整的测试覆盖 (10 个场景)\n\n✅ **T-005**: AuthMiddleware 中间件\n- Authorization header 提取与 Bearer 格式验证\n- Token 验证与 claims 传递\n- 错误响应 (401 UNAUTHORIZED/TOKEN_EXPIRED)\n- 完整的测试覆盖 (9 个场景)\n\n✅ **T-006**: /v1 路由组注册 AuthMiddleware\n- jwtManager 初始化与配置注入\n- 中间件栈顺序：Logger → Recovery → AuthMiddleware → ConcurrencyLimit\n- /health 端点保持公开\n- 集成测试验证\n\n✅ **T-007**: Outbound JWT 签发回归验证\n- proxy.go 中 forwardToSandbox 保持原有 outbound JWT 签发逻辑 (Sandbox/SandboxClaimKind)\n- CodeInterpreter 不携带 Authorization header\n\n✅ **T-008**: 编译与测试门禁\n- go build ./pkg/router/... 通过\n- go test ./pkg/router/... 全部通过 (30 个测试用例)\n- go test -race 无 data race\n- T/C 比率：2799/1647 ≈ 1.7 > 0.4\n\n---\n\n### **Deferred (无延期)**\n\n本次变更所有任务均已完成，无延期项。\n\n---\n\n**验证结果**: 所有测试通过 (30/30)，编译通过，无 race condition。","time":{"start":1775852393734,"end":1775852393734}}}
